            \ "silent normal gv\<Plug>(EasyAlign)*="<CR>`z
nnoremap <silent> <Leader>: mzvip:<C-U>silent '<,'>EasyAlign*:>l1<CR>`z
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>: mz:<C-U>silent '<,'>EasyAlign*:>l1<CR>`z

" Python and vim comments
