vmap <silent> <Leader># :mz<C-u>execute
            \ "silent normal gv\<Plug>(EasyAlign)*#"<CR>`z
nmap <silent> <Leader>" :execute "silent normal mz\<Plug>(EasyAlign)ip*\"`z"<CR>
